      "id": "PopularPost8095",
      "post_content": "Obviously not as good as cards like [Brainstorm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Brainstorm) or [Ponder](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ponder), but this card is very fun in formats where players draw from the same deck (like DC10). The fact the cards you choose from your hand don't have to be one of the three cards drawn is quite good too (making this card superior to cards like [Portent](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Portent)). 2.5/5 stars.",
      "posted_by": "kitsunewarlock",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost8095\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">Obviously not as good as cards like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Brainstorm\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Brainstorm\">Brainstorm</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ponder\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ponder\">Ponder</a>, but this card is very fun in formats where players draw from the same deck (like DC10).  The fact the cards you choose from your hand don't have to be one of the three cards drawn is quite good too (making this card superior to cards like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Portent\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Portent\">Portent</a>).  2.5/5 stars.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '8095'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy486\">kitsunewarlock</span>\r\n                                (6/2/2009 12:59:27 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_s